<ComponentApiDoc Type="typeof(HxGrid<object>)">
    <MainContent>
        <p class="lead">
            Displays tabular data from data source. Includes support for client-side and server-side paging &amp; sorting (or virtualized scrolling as needed).
        </p>

        <h3>No paging &amp; sorting or client-side paging &amp; sorting</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Create a field/property for the data.</li>
            <li>Set data to this field/property. Do not sort data.</li>
            <li>Use the extension method <code>ApplyTo</code> (<code>request.ApplyTo(data)</code>) in the <code>@nameof(HxGrid<object>.DataProvider)</code> method to automaticky sort and page data from the field/property. While the result of the <code>@nameof(HxGrid<object>.DataProvider)</code> method is a generic <code>Task</code>, the result must be wrapped using <code>Task.FromResult</code>. It is easy, see the demo source code.</li>
        </ul>
        <Demo Type="typeof(HxGrid_ClientSideDemo)" />

        <h3>Server side paging &amp; sorting</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Implement the <code>@nameof(HxGrid<object>.DataProvider)</code> method to delegate the paging &amp; sorting to the server side. The sample code does not have this implementation.</li>
        </ul>
        <Demo Type="typeof(HxGrid_ServerSideDemo)" />

        <h3>Empty data</h3>
        <Demo Type="typeof(HxGrid_EmptyDataDemo)" />

        <h3>Virtualized</h3>
        <HxAlert Color="ThemeColor.Warning"><HxIcon Icon="@BootstrapIcon.ExclamationTriangleFill" /> The <code>ItemRowHeight</code> parameter has to be set for the virtualization to work properly. The default value is 50 pixels.</HxAlert>
        <Demo Type="typeof(HxGrid_VirtualizedDemo)" />
    </MainContent>
	<CssVariables>
        <ComponentApiDocCssVariable Name="--hx-grid-button-hover-background" Default="#dee2e6">
            Grid button background color on hover.
        </ComponentApiDocCssVariable>
        <ComponentApiDocCssVariable Name="--hx-grid-button-border-radius" Default=".2rem">
            Grid button border radius.
        </ComponentApiDocCssVariable>
        <ComponentApiDocCssVariable Name="--hx-pager-margin" Default="1rem">
            Pager margin.
        </ComponentApiDocCssVariable>
    </CssVariables>
</ComponentApiDoc>

